{"tid":918524,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Play 毒 App 被下載超 58 萬次，Google 後知後覺急下架！","createTime":"2018-11-27T09:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T15:28:53.000Z","uid":59499,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d05bdb70df7fc7c9a8a1442414d1300f6140fd3a","tid":918524,"uid":59499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:43:48.000Z","msg":"手機應用平台雖然給我們帶來方便，但也隱藏著風險。 Google Play 作為全球流量最大的應用平台，而且也是 Google 官方的下載平台，但依然無法杜絕惡意軟件。最近，ESET 公司安全研究員 Lukas Stefanko 在 Twitter上曝光 13 款 Google Play 應用上偽裝成賽車遊戲的惡意軟件。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/google-play-malware-fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fgoogle-play-malware-fb.jpg&h=ecdabf4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據 Lukas Stefanko 在 Twitter 上表示，出問題的遊戲程序共有 13 款，它們都來自一個域名在伊斯坦布爾的應用開發者。當用戶下載這 13 個偽裝成遊戲的惡意軟件後，這些 APP 不會顯示圖標，用戶沒辦法從桌面找到卸載它們，並且它們還會自動下載一些惡意軟件並引導用戶安裝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/26dfc0f98213eaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F26dfc0f98213eaa.jpg&h=f5d597a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前， Google Play 已經收到了惡意軟件舉報，並移除了這些惡意軟件，但在Google Play 將其下架之前，這些惡意軟件的安裝次數總計已經超過 58 萬次。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/908d66bca4f505f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F908d66bca4f505f.jpg&h=e880c090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相比封閉的 iOS 系統，Apple 的做法是先審批才上架以確保被用戶下載的 Apps 安全。而 Android 系統由於是開放體系，一般都是上架後被發現問題才會移除，所以安全性一直都是為人詬病。當然，Google 一直都在改進篩查機制和技術，單單去年 Google Play 就刪除了多達 70 萬個惡意應用程序。希望，Google 能再接再厲，給用戶帶來更好的應用環境。"},{"pid":"6bb6e4cc7e0eefc6c5c96ac6bb7b3a1d79787cfc","tid":918524,"uid":171668,"like":28,"dislike":59,"score":-31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"1）iOS咁自閉，寧願俾人hack都唔撚用iPhone<br />\n2）用得Android就肯定會小心，一定唔會響Play Store down app，只會上網睇晒review+youtube，確定無事先至自己下載黎裝。<br />\n3）用Android個個都工程師，你估係挨瘋人頭豬咩"},{"pid":"55897f29f34badb8c08171a1eaec7d4c4d4bf10f","tid":918524,"uid":161374,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6bb6e4cc7e0eefc6c5c96ac6bb7b3a1d79787cfc","tid":918524,"uid":171668,"like":28,"dislike":59,"score":-31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"1）iOS咁自閉，寧願俾人hack都唔撚用iPhone<br />\n2）用得Android就肯定會小心，一定唔會響Play Store down app，只會上網睇晒review+youtube，確定無事先至自己下載黎裝。<br />\n3）用Android個個都工程師，你估係挨瘋人頭豬咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"小心比an狗咬"},{"pid":"a88268fefbdfdfec24ace630c3b468d48c4e965f","tid":918524,"uid":34939,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"55897f29f34badb8c08171a1eaec7d4c4d4bf10f","tid":918524,"uid":161374,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6bb6e4cc7e0eefc6c5c96ac6bb7b3a1d79787cfc","tid":918524,"uid":171668,"like":28,"dislike":59,"score":-31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"1）iOS咁自閉，寧願俾人hack都唔撚用iPhone<br />\n2）用得Android就肯定會小心，一定唔會響Play Store down app，只會上網睇晒review+youtube，確定無事先至自己下載黎裝。<br />\n3）用Android個個都工程師，你估係挨瘋人頭豬咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"小心比an狗咬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"已經有隻入黎咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6673e23a4d1c81749dc853114994354afb3faa65","tid":918524,"uid":10904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bb6e4cc7e0eefc6c5c96ac6bb7b3a1d79787cfc","tid":918524,"uid":171668,"like":28,"dislike":59,"score":-31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"1）iOS咁自閉，寧願俾人hack都唔撚用iPhone<br />\n2）用得Android就肯定會小心，一定唔會響Play Store down app，只會上網睇晒review+youtube，確定無事先至自己下載黎裝。<br />\n3）用Android個個都工程師，你估係挨瘋人頭豬咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"曲到直"},{"pid":"0d05fdf29a6aa9fbe58851b19ed15d3e0c83f4c0","tid":918524,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20